name: Shakib Al Hasan
about: Shakib Al Hasan is a Bangladeshi cricketer and current captain of the Bangladesh national cricket team.

name: Virat Kohli
about: Virat Kohli is an Indian international cricketer and the former captain of the Indian national cricket team.

name: Babar Azam
about: Mohammad Babar Azam is a Pakistani international cricketer and captain of the Pakistan national cricket team.

name: AB de Villiers
about: Abraham Benjamin de Villiers is a former South African international cricketer.

name: Mustafizur Rahman
about: Mustafizur Rahman is a Bangladeshi international cricketer. He is a left-arm fast-medium bowler.

name: Kieron Pollard
about: Kieron Adrian Pollard is a former West Indies cricketer. He has captained the West Indies cricket team in limited overs cricket.

name: Rashid Khan
about: Rashid Khan Arman is an Afghan international cricketer and captain of the Afghanistan national team in T20I format.

name: Taskin Ahmed
about: Taskin Ahmed Tazim is a Bangladeshi cricketer. He is a right-arm fast bowler and a left-handed batsman.

name: Ben Stokes
about: Benjamin Andrew Stokes OBE is an English international cricketer who is the captain of the England Test team.

name: Hardik Pandya
about: Hardik Himanshu Pandya is an Indian international cricketer who is the current vice-captain of the Indian cricket team in limited overs.

name: Shaheen Afridi
about: Shaheen Shah Afridi is a Pakistani professional cricketer who plays as a fast bowler for the Pakistan national cricket team.

name: Devon Conway
about: Devon Philip Conway is a New Zealand cricketer and hard hitter batsman. He usually plays onedown.

name: Marcus Stoinis
about: Marcus Peter Stoinis is an Australian all rounder who plays limited overs cricket for the Australian national team.

name: Jos Buttler
about: Joseph Charles Buttler MBE is an English cricketer who is the captain of the England cricket team in limited overs cricket.

name: Glenn Maxwell
about: Glenn James Maxwell is an Australian professional cricketer and all-rounder who bats right handed and bowl off break.

name: Jasprit Bumrah
about: Jasprit Jasbirsingh Bumrah is an Indian international cricketer who plays all formats of the game.

name: Rahkeem Cornwall
about: Rahkeem Rashawn Shane Cornwall is an Antiguan cricketer. A right-arm off-break bowler, Cornwall has played for Leeward Islands cricket team.

name: Azam Khan
about: Azam Khan is a Pakistani cricketer. Known as a power-hitter. His international debut in July 2021.
